Each Cloud Provider integrations with New Relic lets you monitor your data in New Relic in the form of New Relic entities and dashboards. 
New Relic gives its customers upto date monitoring of their cloud services in form of entities. 

This document will guide you which services are converted to entities in different cloud providers.

## Amazon Integrations

New Relic provides Amazon integrations through [AWS CloudWatch Metric Streams and API Polling](/docs/infrastructure/amazon-integrations/connect/aws-metric-stream/). The recommendation is to [enable Cloudwatch metric streams integrations](/docs/infrastructure/amazon-integrations/connect/aws-metric-stream-setup) as it covers broader range of AWS services.
